Introduction

Son Ga In is a South Korean singer, actress, model and entertainer under Mystic Story Entertainment (a subsidiary label of SM Entertainment). She is currently main dancer, vocalist, visual, face of the group and maknae in Brown Eyed Girls . She debuted as a solo artist on October 8, 2010.
